entries.complete: pcontrast1 CorSec Command: <pcontrast3  You OK, pilot? We weren't expecting such a swift response. Come on back to the station for debriefing.pcontrast1  >
entries.title: Corellia System: Eliminate the Cloak Surprise Attack
entries.title_d: A wing of Cloak fighters arrived in retribution for intercepting the stolen information they were supposed to receive. Eliminate them.
